I would like a JIRA issue to appear every day it is "active" rather than simply once as defined by its Due Date as currently.

I use JIRA issues to define project tasks e.g. Bespoke webservice. These tasks get assigned a duration e.g. 5d. They finally get a Due Date. What I would like is to be able to set a task with a duration and due date and see that task repeated for the days entered up to the due date.

